              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div>
                <h3>Determine</h3>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </section>

  <section class="services-intro">
    <div class="wrap wrap-center wrap-center-narrow">
      <div class="section-spaced">
        <div class="section-summary">
          <h1 class="section-heading">Why Would You Need Sales Material?</h1>
        </div>
        <div>
          <ul class="section-list section-list-bullets">
            <li>Your business is located in a specific geographic location and you want your  message to be seen by as large an audience as possible within that community</li>
            <li>You have a larger budget and want to amplify your marketing efforts with further brand awareness</li>
            <li>You want an attention-grabbing way to get people to share and spread your message on social media.</li>
            <li>You have a large target audience that is frequently within a specific location where a broad message would garner a large amount of repeated exposure and potential interest in your message.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
