            <li>It makes people want to share it on social media</li>
            <li>Its simple and easy to quickly take in</li>
            <li>Its in a great, high traffic location</li>
            <li>Its eye-catching and attention grabbing</li>
            <li>Its intriguing and provokes further investigation</li>
          </ul>
